{"tid":672890,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實籍同藉係咪真係咁難分？","createTime":"2018-05-21T11:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T17:45:41.000Z","uid":79651,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d7be4939b1fe9d11f954b3763e00fa495fd7929b","tid":672890,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"成日都見人用錯「籍」同「藉」，寫「籍口」同「書藉」，真係咁難分咩？以下嘅定義係跟說文解字。<br />\n<br />\n籍者，簿書也。 一般嚟講，個「籍」字會令人聯想到一本本嘅嘢，例如：書籍、戶籍、籍貫<br />\n<br />\n藉者，祭藉也。原本係關以前祭祀嘅事，係祭品嚟，後來用法同「借」差唔多，例如：藉口、藉著<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好再用錯喇好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日見到人用錯都覺得好礙眼<br />\n<br />\n歡迎學術J 補充"},{"pid":"9da893f46074ad2b1e67dc59851af288e655d153","tid":672890,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f12062fd9c800e3e449aaeca66c08d75d076252","tid":672890,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63c3b5ef80550a36c5d1c8ada13f9860e1771bdd","tid":672890,"uid":88988,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根 跟 都好礙眼"},{"pid":"d139ad2a3019e5406ad84006099d8b0f95afec58","tid":672890,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"895305adb35fcb6bf4a680043f0f63f7bb195aa1","tid":672890,"uid":118823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"好簡單：中國古代既書係竹簡 --&gt; 書「籍」係竹花頭<br />\n<br />\n利申：中學文言文背默N次食蛋"},{"pid":"aeba7d349d71b5c89f377d0eb2f337a158a579fc","tid":672890,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"明明唔難分 但呢人往往不求甚解 亂鳩咁用"},{"pid":"75e9612450df99d834989a3c6e2277b9810294a1","tid":672890,"uid":134774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"可能班人打拼音然後懶到次